{"word":"G2534 - καίγε - kaíge - kah'-ee-gheh - And","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καίγε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kaíge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kah'-ee-gheh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">And</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"உம், அல்லவா - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"and, at least"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2532 - καί - kaí - kahee/2532\">G2532</a> and <a href=\"#/G1065 - γέ - gé - gheh/1065\">G1065</a>; <i>and at least</i> (or <i>even</i>, <i>indeed</i>): - and, at least.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}